{"tid":1758778,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連格透露1歲時已經穿上曼聯球衣，拒絕加盟曼城利物浦","createTime":"2019-11-27T09:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T10:49:43.000Z","uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"217b0f8f7f7331d1b15abba220d919e3881c1a1a","tid":1758778,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"聯中場連格是球隊的青訓產品，原來在他加盟曼聯前，曾經拒絕了曼城和利物浦的邀請。<br />\n<br />\n這位 26 歲英格蘭中場於 7 歲加入曼聯青年軍，他透露當時自己有很多選擇，包括曼城、愛華頓、利物浦等球會都對他有興趣，不過，連格稱自己 1 歲時已經穿上曼聯球衣拍照，認為曼聯才是自己的家，最終與「紅魔鬼」簽約。<br />\n<br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n雖然表現經常受到球迷批評，但是，連格仍然會樂觀面對，他表示不會看網上的評論，又指看得太多社交網絡，會令小將不知道自己有多好。<br />\n<br />\n連格於 2014/15 球季於英超亮相，至今為球隊上陣 183 場，並攻入 29 球。"},{"pid":"508b01d64f9aebae3808fa4f004d9e499166d250","tid":1758778,"uid":23655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"啲弱智仔不嬲樂觀"},{"pid":"e5e1450cc7bc2269e492ad4134a6b7a1ab109d3c","tid":1758778,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"根正苗紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b56a271914bdc230ef4adc1d28c12d6bb23fb6e","tid":1758778,"uid":60695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"他表示不會看網上的評論，又指看得太多社交網絡，會令小將不知道自己有多好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b6b8c51ee77a57a20f40eaae397e75eebc302f","tid":1758778,"uid":30768,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"嚇死利鏝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5942459dfe6358e6025fd92d25dca1b70ca9a69f","tid":1758778,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"JLINGZ🤟🏻🤟🏻🤟🏻🤟🏻"